              <li>Changes take effect immediately upon confirmation</li>
              <li>Billing is adjusted automatically on a prorated basis</li>
              <li>Upgrades are charged immediately for the remaining billing period</li>
              <li>Downgrades generate a prorated credit applied to the next invoice</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>9.2 Cancellation</h3>
